```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User/UI
  participant API as Search API
  participant OS as OpenSearch (BM25)
  participant QD as Qdrant (Vectors)
  participant RR as Reranker
  participant RAG as RAG Orchestrator
  participant LLM as LLM Provider

  U->>API: Query + filters

  par Retrieval
    API->>OS: BM25 top-k
    API->>QD: ANN top-k
  end

  API->>RR: Fuse + rerank
  RR-->>API: top-n

  API->>RAG: build context (chunks)
  RAG->>LLM: prompt(context + question)
  LLM-->>RAG: draft answer
  RAG-->>API: answer + citations
  API-->>U: response
```
